his time when creative ideas start to dry up and you need some quick inspiration. Maybe you’ve still got a few people on your list who are impossible to shop for. Or maybe you’ve decided to treat yourself this year (anything to hit that free shipping minimum, right?).\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eLuckily our shop is packed with hundreds of thoughtful \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/gifts\"\u003eideas\u003c/a\u003e—and our curated \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/p/holiday-gift-guides-2024\"\u003egift guides\u003c/a\u003e make finding the perfect pick a whole lot easier. And even better, our team shared what they’re adding to their own wishlists. From a genius citrus juicer to the ultimate frying pan, these are the gifts we’re giving (and crossing our fingers to get) this year.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \u003ch3\u003e1. \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/12121-fredericks-and-mae-large-plastic-cutting-board\"\u003eFredericks \u0026amp; Mae Multi Confetti Board\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/h3\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e“The Fredericks and Mae Multi Confetti Board. The colors are so perfect it would make me happy to meal prep.” —\u003cem\u003eKelly Kenneally, Graphic Designer\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003ca data-vendor-id=\"698\" data-vendor-name=\"Fredericks \u0026amp; Mae\" data-category-name=\"Cutting Boards\" data-price=\"40.0\" data-ga-event-label=\"Creative: 12121\" data-product-id=\"12121\" data-product-name=\"Multicolor Plastic Cutting Board\" data-url=\"/shop/products/12121-fredericks-and-mae-large-plastic-cutting-board\" data-img=\"https://images.food52.com/PdRxuQahyIBoW_RbjA--9La19c4=/470x470/9f7637ea-9a44-47e7-9ff7-b2075d38a6ac--2023-0725_fredricks-and-mae_large-cutting-board_multi-confetti_silo_1x1_ty-mecham.jpg\" data-sku-id=\"\" data-price-range=\"\u0026lt;span\u0026gt;$40\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;–\u0026lt;span\u0026gt;$145\u0026lt;/span\u002